This WotLK Fun Server has been built with education as the main purpose and our team would like to keep it that way.

Since any public and/or commercial use of this software is considered illegal in many countries, 
(please refer to your local law) our team will not provide any help nor support with such usage in any way.

Every user of this software is encouraged to make sure no law is being broken on his/her side.
Our team will not take any responsibility of any kind for the usage of this software by the end users.